  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK699">
<l>koḷappaṭṭē meṉṟeṇṇik koḷḷāta ceyyār</l>
<l>tuḷakkaṟṟa kāṭci yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose judgement is firm will not do what is disagreeable (to the sovereign) saying (within themselves) "We are esteemed by the king".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
